description:
Glad OdorShield Trash Bags in Moonlight Breeze Scent provide strength plus odor control, to keep your home smelling fresh and clean. These kitchen garbage bags are made with OdorShield technology and Febreze with Gain Moonlight Breeze for guaranteed 5 day odor control, based on lab test compared to unscented bags. The unique diamond pattern in these drawstring bags, stretches around objects to prevent rips and the reinforcing bands help add strength while reducing plastic waste, when compared to a leading branded bag. These trash can liners are reinforced at the top, middle and bottom and are made with thicker plastic for leak protection. With the 3 ply drawstring, which grips the can, the bag stays in place until you are ready to take it out. The drawstring bag makes closing and carrying easy. These 13 gallon size, odor eliminating, trash bags, fit tall kitchen trash cans, and are perfect for use in kitchens or seasonal cleaning like Spring Cleaning and Back to School.

Usage Directions: Lift the trash bag from the container by pulling the drawstrings on either side of the bag. Knot the drawstrings for added security. Carry the bag by the drawstring and toss into garbage.

Caution Statements: Plastic bags can be dangerous. To avoid danger of suffocation, keep all plastic bags away from babies and children. DO NOT USE FOR FOOD STORAGE.
